# Performance / Core Web Vitals

Protect LCP, INP, CLS on PLP/PDP/cart/checkout/home.

## Do

- `next/image` for product/hero images with correct sizes/priority for LCP hero only
- Reserve aspect ratio space to prevent CLS
- Keep checkout light — minimal animation, minimal third-party
- Defer non-critical JS; avoid shipping GSAP on checkout routes if unused
- Server Components by default; client islands only where needed
- Cache public catalog reads carefully; never cache private cart HTML

## Don't

- Unsized images / layout-shifting banners
- Huge client carousels on first paint
- Blocking third-party scripts in checkout
- Animate LCP element from opacity 0 without SSR-visible fallback

Measure before “optimizing.” Prefer deleting JS over micro-tweaks.
